SOURCES - What have you learned from researching in pairs?
The Sources panel lets you see all the scripts that are part of the inspected page.
Standard controls to pause, resume, and step through code are provided below the panel selection icons
A button to force a pause at exceptions is located at the bottom of the window.
Sources are visible in separate tabs and clicking  opens the file navigator which will display all open scripts.
